node.text: A Very Happy birthday to THE SUCIDE SQUAD’S Brilliant Director , JAMES  GUNN !  And he has inadvertently given me a great present too ! ROCKY (1976) 92% Rocky Balboa vs. Apollo Creed Here the most influential and iconic bout in the history ofHollywood. Rocky's battle with Apollo Creed has been reworked in countless ways across numerous genres; it's evoked in virtually every scrappy-underdog tale. However, none have been quite able to match the original for spine- tingling tension Even its over-familiarity (it plays on Jumbotrons in sports arenas virtually every night) hasn't dulled its impact; in addition to being oreathlessy exciting and dramatically potent, it doesn't end quite the way you'd expect. M Rocky Balboa Vs Apollo Creed'.

node.text: Very proud that ROTTEN TOMATOES has chosen Rocky versus Apollo Creed as the greatest fight scene in the history of cinema!  It has been incredible honor to have created this character and The joy it has brought  for decades.! But ROCKY VS DRAGO COMING this November,  to me was is the hardest accomplishment of all … KEEP PUNCHING!  #carlweathers. #dolphlungren #mgm
